The evidence with the title 'The U.S. owes China this much debt ' says Oct 26, 2017  ... The U.S. debt to China is $ 1.2 trillion as of august 2017. That's 30 percent of the $ 3.05 trillion in Treasury bills, notes, and bonds held by foreign countries. The rest of the $ 20 trillion national debt is owned by either the American people or by the U.S. government itself . China holds more than the $1.1 trillion  ... 
